  "title": "Corporate Secretary Executive |  Marymount - YZ11",
  "description": "<p><strong>Corporate secretary executive </strong></p><p>Location:  [ Marymount ]<br />Working Days: Mon-Fri , 5 days<br />Working hours : 9am to 6pm<br /><em>Salary:</em> $2500 - $3000 </p><p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>To provide full suite of corporate secretarial related services (e.g., incorporation of company, change of company officers and share transfers)</li><li>Handling submission of ACRA & IRAS transactions</li><li>Preparing Directors/Shareholders resolutions, Extraordinary / Annual General Meetings Minutes, relevant statutory forms and other related documents for on-going corporate secretarial matters.</li><li>Ensure that secretarial files and statutory records are properly updated and maintained</li><li>Performing Onboarding / Ongoing Due Diligence Check on new and existing clients</li><li>Any other corporate and ad-hoc jobs as required</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma/Advanced Diploma/Degree in relevant field, Business Administration, Business Management or Law</li><li>Prior relevant corporate secretarial experience will be an advantage</li></ul><p><br />Tan Yen Zhen (Chen Yan Zhen) Reg No: R25138932</p><p>The SupremeHR Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279</p>",
